name: Custom table functionality using table shell recipe mode

steps.name: Open result and set up view
Wait for selector getByTestId(/^item-name/).filter({ hasText: '1771957521653 substantiate-e2e' }).first().or(getByTestId('empty-list-message'))
Fill "1771957684303 Descriptive Analysis Plan_Report - 1771957573131 Descriptive Cohort (Patients)" getByTestId('tree-search')

Wait for selector getByTestId(/^item-name/).filter({ hasText: '1771957684303 Descriptive Analysis Plan_Report - 1771957573131 Descriptive Cohort (Patients)' }).first().or(getByTestId('empty-list-message'))
Click getByTestId(/^item-name/).filter({ hasText: '1771957684303 Descriptive Analysis Plan_Report - 1771957573131 Descriptive Cohort (Patients)' }).first()
Create, generate and validate custom tables using table shell recipe mode

Hover getByTestId(/^widget-/).filter({ has: getByTestId('widget-header-wrapper').getByTestId('widget-header').getByText('Analytic Cohort', { exact: true }) }).locator('table tbody:nth-of-type(1) > tr:nth-of-type(1) > td:nth-of-type(2)').first()

Hover getByTestId(/^widget-/).filter({ has: getByTestId('widget-header-wrapper').getByTestId('widget-header').getByText('Analytic Cohort', { exact: true }) }).locator('table tbody:nth-of-type(2) > tr:nth-of-type(1) > td:nth-of-type(2)').first()
Switch views, regenerate and observe warnings/errors
Click locator('table > tbody > tr').filter({ hasText: '1771958159153 Temporary Table' }).getByTestId('dropdown-menu')
Click locator('table > tbody > tr').filter({ hasText: '1771958159153 Temporary Table' }).getByTestId('customTable-delete')
Expect "toBeHidden" locator('table > tbody > tr').filter({ hasText: '1771958159153 Temporary Table' })
